Big mouth!

82
00:09:18,700 --> 00:09:21,300
For such a risky matter,

83
00:09:21,300 --> 00:09:23,300
I shouldn't have called on Lin Xiuya.

84
00:09:23,300 --> 00:09:25,900
His parents died at the hands of the Soul Hall.

85
00:09:25,900 --> 00:09:30,200
If anything happens to him,
I won't be able to forgive myself.

86
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:35,200
What about it? I still haven't forgiven you yet.
You two didn't let me go with you.

87
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:37,300
Exactly. You didn't bring me along either.

88
00:09:37,300 --> 00:09:40,400
You think that I'm not good enough.
You look down on me.

89
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:43,400
You probably thought I'd be a burden, didn't you?

90
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:45,620
If you know the answer, why ask the question?

91
00:09:45,620 --> 00:09:47,200
You.

92
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:49,600
No, I didn't mean it that way.

93
00:09:53,740 --> 00:09:57,090
I was just worried about your safety.

94
00:09:58,500 --> 00:10:02,000
When you were locked up,
the seniors came to beat us up.

95
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:05,970
They took away all the energy talismans we got
from the Black Point Region.

96
00:10:06,900 --> 00:10:11,000
Lin Xiuya told me that he was afraid
that you'd react impulsively once you knew.

97
00:10:12,500 --> 00:10:16,200
It'll be fine. I'll go and look for them again.

98
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:18,300
See? You're not bringing us along with you again.

99
00:10:18,300 --> 00:10:20,200
If you're going to go and be a hero by yourself,

100
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:22,400
you don't need this group of brothers.

101
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:26,400
As your brothers, we do have our usefulness.

102
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:28,800
I said I didn't mean it that way.

103
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:36,300
I remember I closed the door.

104
00:10:47,300 --> 00:10:49,700
Where's my Mystical Heavy Ruler?

105
00:10:53,300 --> 00:10:55,100
What are you saying?

106
00:10:55,100 --> 00:10:59,200
Where did you take my weapon to?

107
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,500
I...

108
00:11:02,500 --> 00:11:03,600
It's not with me here.

109
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:05,900
Where is it?!

110
00:11:08,700 --> 00:11:11,700
It's with my teacher. I'll go get it.

111
00:11:11,700 --> 00:11:13,700
I'll send it to you tomorrow.

112
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:18,500
Tomorrow night, come to
the Martial Arts Transfer Forest to find me.

113
00:11:18,500 --> 00:11:21,400
Bring the Mystical Heavy Ruler
in exchange for your friend.

114
00:11:21,400 --> 00:11:25,200
If you play any tricks,
you will all have to die!

115
00:12:16,900 --> 00:12:20,940
I brought your weapon. Release my friend.

116
00:12:23,900 --> 00:12:26,600
Your lousy weapon is so heavy.

117
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:28,910
I wonder how you can possibly use it.

118
00:12:28,910 --> 00:12:34,300
You want it? Come back with me to explain
to the Sect Leader. You will be rewarded.

119
00:12:34,300 --> 00:12:35,920
How about your dozens of disciples?

120
00:12:35,920 --> 00:12:39,120
They couldn't keep this secret,
but let you find out about it.

121
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:41,270
Their Fight Qi has all been abolished.

122
00:12:41,270 --> 00:12:43,950
They deserved it!

123
00:12:56,900 --> 00:13:00,620
But if I can bring back a disciple
from the Xiao family,

124
00:13:00,620 --> 00:13:03,890
it will indeed be a good gift for the Sect Leader.

125
00:13:03,890 --> 00:13:07,790
I will go and look for him myself.
I don't need to trouble you.

126
00:13:09,900 --> 00:13:13,290
Release my friend.
I have already brought your object here.

127
00:13:13,290 --> 00:13:17,000
If you don't follow me,
then you'll just have to die along with him!

128
00:13:49,180 --> 00:13:52,010
Fire-Splitting Wave-Devouring Ruler!

129
00:13:54,300 --> 00:13:58,800
That was the first form.
Now witness my second form!

130
00:14:10,700 --> 00:14:14,520
Not possible. This is not possible!

131
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:26,680
Of course, adults never abide by their words.

132
00:14:26,680 --> 00:14:28,980
Watch me use Form 3!

133
00:14:28,980 --> 00:14:30,770
I'm not ready yet.

134
00:16:02,100 --> 00:16:05,810
That was really dangerously close.

135
00:16:07,100 --> 00:16:12,350
Medicine Elder, your Fight Qi is too powerful.

136
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:22,660
Are you all right? Did he torture you?

137
00:16:22,660 --> 00:16:25,550
What do you think?
I've been hung upside down for one whole day.

138
00:16:25,550 --> 00:16:27,330
My legs are numb already.

139
00:16:29,400 --> 00:16:32,620
Are you all right? Do you want me to carry you?

140
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:37,430
Why is your Fight Qi so awesome?

141
00:16:37,430 --> 00:16:40,890
I told you, that it only works on certain occasions.

142
00:16:40,890 --> 00:16:42,960
Don't ask.

143
00:16:49,900 --> 00:16:54,420
You've just progressed to the Fight Master stage. That's why
you couldn't hold out and your vital channel got wounded.

144
00:16:55,400 --> 00:16:57,790
I really want to become stronger as quickly as I can.

145
00:16:57,790 --> 00:17:01,860
I don't ever want to be so passive when facing the enemy.

146
00:17:01,860 --> 00:17:05,400
Don't be so anxious, lad. I will help you heal first.
When you have recovered,

147
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:08,430
you will immediately begin to train
on the second form of Flame-Splitting Wave-Devouring Ruler.

148
00:17:08,430 --> 00:17:10,230
