149
00:17:33,599 --> 00:17:36,779
Last night, the elders asked dozens of students.

150
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:42,860
Some students said they saw Xiao Yan fighting
with the envoy of the Soul Hall.

151
00:17:42,860 --> 00:17:44,630
And they were evenly matched.

152
00:17:44,630 --> 00:17:49,560
If one or two said so,
I would think they were crazy.

153
00:17:49,560 --> 00:17:52,630
But when dozens of people say the same thing,

154
00:17:52,630 --> 00:17:55,360
could they have lost their minds collectively?

155
00:17:56,700 --> 00:18:00,580
How many of us went out to find Lin Xiuya yesterday?

156
00:18:02,070 --> 00:18:05,260
To prepare for the attack from the Soul Hall,

157
00:18:05,260 --> 00:18:10,370
one elder brought a whole team of senior students
to find him and they failed.

158
00:18:10,370 --> 00:18:15,020
But he brought the person back so easily.
How did he do it?

159
00:18:15,020 --> 00:18:19,190
Lin Xiuya was gravely injured
and Xiao Yan was also slightly injured.

160
00:18:19,190 --> 00:18:22,240
I asked them to go back to their dormitory to recuperate.

161
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:24,220
I asked him the same question.

162
00:18:24,220 --> 00:18:27,490
He said that he was just lucky.

163
00:18:27,490 --> 00:18:30,530
Does Elder Mi believe that?

164
00:18:32,600 --> 00:18:36,980
In my opinion, we should summon these two
to the elders' compound.

165
00:18:36,980 --> 00:18:41,400
Watch them very closely so that
they can not corroborate their statements beforehand.

166
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:44,870
What do you think?

167
00:18:45,590 --> 00:18:48,060
Xiao Yan, this kid.

168
00:18:48,060 --> 00:18:52,530
Last time, when he was in my class,
he was already a 9-star Fight Practitioner.

169
00:18:52,530 --> 00:18:55,160
But to compare that to the envoy of the Soul Hall,

170
00:18:55,160 --> 00:18:58,270
he is just a tiny flea.

171
00:18:58,270 --> 00:19:03,280
That's to say that there is still
an expert that we haven't seen yet.

172
00:19:04,230 --> 00:19:08,470
I went to the woods to look at the marks
at the scene where they fought.

173
00:19:08,470 --> 00:19:10,890
That Fight Qi,

174
00:19:10,890 --> 00:19:15,020
