he left a handprint near the name of the academy
which was written by the Fight God.

181
00:19:37,300 --> 00:19:38,990
I have chipped it out.

182
00:19:38,990 --> 00:19:40,560
What handprint?

183
00:20:08,200 --> 00:20:11,290
This is someone at the level of Fight Ancestor.

184
00:20:11,290 --> 00:20:14,190
This matter... That's even more strange.

185
00:20:14,190 --> 00:20:16,770
Xiao Yan is only a 9-star Fight Practitioner.

186
00:20:16,770 --> 00:20:20,720
How dare he challenge a high-level Master
from the Soul Hall?

187
00:20:22,800 --> 00:20:25,360
And according to everyone at the scene,

188
00:20:25,360 --> 00:20:28,660
the two of them were evenly matched.

189
00:20:28,660 --> 00:20:33,980
Could Xiao Yan have also entered some cult organization?

190
00:20:35,100 --> 00:20:39,460
Xiao Yan's fight techniques are
from the Star Fall Pavilion and the Xiao family.

191
00:20:39,460 --> 00:20:42,680
There's no suspicion.

192
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:45,400
But I think the first question here is...

193
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:50,600
Who was it who brought the envoy
from the Soul Hall to the academy?

194
00:20:54,600 --> 00:20:57,780
Except for the dozens of students
that Lei Xiong admitted,

195
00:20:57,780 --> 00:21:00,120
who else could it be?

196
00:21:00,800 --> 00:21:03,000
We don't know that yet.

197
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:07,520
We don't even know how long
they have stayed here in the academy.

198
00:21:12,600 --> 00:21:16,810
The darkness is coming.

199
00:21:17,700 --> 00:21:20,170
The world will become chaotic again.

200
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:29,690
Do you think Mi Tengshan and Xiao Yan
are in this together?

201
00:21:29,690 --> 00:21:33,790
Every time I said I was going to investigate Xiao Yan,
he always changed the subject.

202
00:21:33,790 --> 00:21:36,990
And then it's over, what's all that about?

203
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:42,300
How the envoy from the Soul Hall got into the academy
is not something that can be investigated.

204
00:21:42,300 --> 00:21:45,720
If we do and there is no result,

205
00:21:45,720 --> 00:21:48,430
how do we account for it?

206
00:21:48,430 --> 00:21:52,930
In the future, what student
would want to stay at the academy?

207
00:21:52,930 --> 00:21:55,660
And if the news gets to the Royal Family,

208
00:21:55,660 --> 00:21:58,220
how do we tell them?

209
00:22:01,300 --> 00:22:05,310
The elders want to minimize the problem

210
00:22:05,310 --> 00:22:07,470
and put an end to the problem.

211
00:22:09,000 --> 00:22:11,390
These old foxes.

212
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:20,570
It's these old foxes who have been working
before we were born.

213
00:22:20,570 --> 00:22:25,150
They are so old that their tails
have grown white hair.

214
00:22:25,150 --> 00:22:27,200
You'll just have to tolerate it.

215
00:23:04,290 --> 00:23:07,530
Brother Xiao Yan, are you washing clothes?

216
00:23:12,320 --> 00:23:14,900
It seems you still haven't accepted your lesson.

217
00:23:16,140 --> 00:23:17,740
What do you mean?

218
00:23:18,560 --> 00:23:22,290
Wherever there's trouble, there's you.
How should I explain it to you?

219
00:23:22,290 --> 00:23:24,120
This isn't the Black Point Region.

220
00:23:24,120 --> 00:23:26,500
Your little comrades are also not here.

221
00:23:26,500 --> 00:23:28,490
You're going to be broken right here today.

222
00:23:28,490 --> 00:23:32,510
In this academy, private fighting isn't allowed.

223
00:23:33,770 --> 00:23:35,780
A private fight?

224
00:23:39,250 --> 00:23:41,610
Two days ago, in here, we

225
00:23:41,610 --> 00:23:44,040
grabbed three of your little comrades.

226
00:23:44,040 --> 00:23:47,250
Lin Xiuya, Hao Tian,

227
00:23:47,250 --> 00:23:52,070
and Hu Jia. We kicked them till they were like
balls rolling all over the floor.

228
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:58,090
They obediently handed over all the stuff they stole
from us in Black Point Region.

229
00:23:58,090 --> 00:24:00,960
Do you know why they don't dare mention it?

230
00:24:04,700 --> 00:24:07,630
It's because they will die much quicker that way.

231
00:24:16,170 --> 00:24:18,440
So, what you mean is...

232
00:24:18,440 --> 00:24:21,570
you also want me to hand over
any and all stolen items?

233
00:24:21,570 --> 00:24:23,330
That is right.

234
00:24:23,330 --> 00:24:26,510
Furthermore, I don't care if you rob other people

235
00:24:26,960 --> 00:24:29,190
or get them from your family,
that is also good.

236
00:24:30,060 --> 00:24:34,780
Every month, you have to give your seniors
10,000 energy talismans.

237
00:24:35,420 --> 00:24:39,120
This request is not too high, right?

238
00:24:39,120 --> 00:24:41,350
- Not high at all.
- Not high at all.

